{"tid":1276761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佔領立法會】湯家驊：這將是歷史上被視為香港失去法治的一天","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T12:25:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"be4b3e65358e68a10b7dff9a7d16857ddece33a5","tid":1276761,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_iaN76_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_iaN76_1200x0.png&h=d5752237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯家驊（圖片來源：民主思路 Facebook）<br />\n<br />\n示威者七一下午開始衝擊立法會大樓，一度佔領立法會會議廳。行政會議成員湯家驊今晨表示，「回歸日 22 周年，將會在歷史上被視為香港失去法治的一天。」又指事件令「我們感到羞愧」，他反問：「不知那些每天把仁義道德、法治自由掛在口邊的人有何感想？」<br />\n<br />\n包括湯家驊在內的行政會議非官守議員，昨晚經由秘書處發出針對「示威者暴力衝擊立法會大樓」聲明，稱「香港是法治的社會，暴力行為向來不為社會所接受。行政會議全體非官守議員強烈譴責示威者以暴力手法衝擊立法會，在大樓內肆意破壞，行為無法無天，嚴重破壞香港優良的法治傳統」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%92-%E9%80%99%E5%B0%87%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%96%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%B1%E5%8E%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%2592-%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%258E%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A4%25A9%2F&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=220cce95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%2592-%25E9%258